Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.21,0:24:09.37,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz-90\pos(30,198)\fsp1}私はただ前を見つめて　生きて行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.51,0:24:15.15,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz-90\pos(30,198)}心に羽根を広げて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.76,0:21:35.55,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz-90\pos(670,198)}落在掌心泪水般的花瓣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.77,0:21:42.58,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz-90\pos(670,198)}摇曳的思念迎风歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.38,0:21:49.75,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz-90\pos(670,198)}会不会有一天让你听到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.31,0:21:56.39,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz-90\pos(670,198)}拉着间断思念的线头
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.80,0:22:03.24,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz-90\pos(670,198)}所剩愿望唯有想见你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.24,0:22:10.35,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz-90\pos(670,198)}追寻淡淡脚印的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.48,0:22:15.69,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz-90\pos(670,198)}哪怕知道这只是徒劳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.88,0:22:23.16,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz-90\pos(670,198)}我是如此珍视你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.16,0:22:28.88,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz-90\pos(670,198)}像花开花谢一样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.88,0:22:36.06,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz-90\pos(670,198)}我会走下去 对 一直这样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.13,0:22:45.21,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz-90\pos(670,198)}始终将你留在心中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.33,0:23:05.09,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz-90\pos(670,198)}眼睑无意流露出的温柔教人心痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.29,0:23:11.94,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz-90\pos(670,198)}好想守护你那笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.94,0:23:19.21,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz-90\pos(670,198)}试着拉开些距离
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.04,0:23:25.86,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz-90\pos(670,198)}为明日所奔忙 破旧的伞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.30,0:23:32.59,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz-90\pos(670,198)}什么才是必要的 会迎来开端吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.60,0:23:39.89,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz-90\pos(670,198)}这样问道 藏于内心的温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.89,0:23:45.28,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz-90\pos(670,198)}那是刚诞生的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.22,0:23:53.48,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\frz-90\pos(670,198)}听到你说总有一天我们会在某处相见
